EVERYONE: Recognize this for what it really is. There is a bot uploading fake torrents, ostensibly to get you to go somewhere to get a password and perhaps get spammed for the rest of your days. The real reason is to do two things. One is a weak attack on the Pirate Bay's reliability by eating up resources and to bog it down. The other is to fuck with the Pirate Bay's reputation. These are paid professional hackers and we can all guess who hired them.  Be careful. Read everything. Look for patterns.
